\sum_{1\leq j\leq k\leq n}(a_kb_k+a_jb_j)=
a_ib_i=A_i
\sum_{1\leq j\leq k\leq n}(A_j+A_k)=
=(A_1+A_1)+
+(A_1+A_2)+(A_2+A_2)+
................................
+(A_1+A_n)+(A_2+A_n)+......+(A_n+A_n)=
=(nA_1+A_1)+((n-1)A_2+2A_2)+......+(A_n+nA_n)=
=(n+1)A_1+(n+1)A_2+...+(n+1)A_n=
=(n+1)(A_1+A_2+...+A_n)=
=(n+1)\sum_{k=1}^{n}A_k=
=(n+1)\sum_{k=1}^{n}a_kb_k
